36:03.856 --> 36:05.463
My God!
I'm so.

36:05.464 --> 36:06.378
Okay, try not to...

36:06.379 --> 36:09.279
Oh, grab this.

36:09.280 --> 36:12.209
Message, I'll get back
to you as soon as possible.

36:12.210 --> 36:15.569
If this message is urgent,
please press three to have...

36:15.570 --> 36:17.449
Stupid door never works.

36:17.450 --> 36:18.303
Well, all right.

36:21.928 --> 36:23.078
Bye.
Take it easy.

36:28.300 --> 36:29.731
Hi, Mom.

36:41.560 --> 36:42.823
