36:43.680 --> 36:46.039
He made me feel so cheap!

36:46.040 --> 36:47.759
I know I made this
decision, but you know what?

36:47.760 --> 36:49.659
It's very hard for me.

36:49.660 --> 36:50.493
Enough.

36:56.748 --> 37:00.489
You have no idea how
hard it is for me, Mom.

37:00.490 --> 37:01.819
I know it's not easy for you,

37:01.820 --> 37:03.837
but it's not easy for me either!

38:12.331 --> 38:13.164
Hello?

38:14.736 --> 38:15.736
Who is it?

38:16.966 --> 38:17.799
Hello?

38:18.640 --> 38:20.286
Hello?

38:20.287 --> 38:21.704
Answer me, hello?

38:22.688 --> 38:24.829
Answer me, please, hello?

38:24.830 --> 38:27.080
Who is it, you know my son?

38:28.143 --> 38:29.143
Hello?

39:15.870 --> 39:16.703
How's school?

39:17.970 --> 39:18.803
Pretty good.

39:30.032 --> 39:30.865
Hey!

39:30.866 --> 39:33.059
Oh, what a surprise, look who's here!

39:33.060 --> 39:33.893
Hi.

39:34.750 --> 39:36.019
Oh, your mother was in this morning.

39:36.020 --> 39:37.719
She had breakfast with my wife.

39:37.720 --> 39:38.680
Yeah?

39:38.681 --> 39:40.049
Rama!
Yeah?

39:40.050 --> 39:41.003
Look who's here.

39:41.004 --> 39:42.141
Hey, Lenie!

40:01.640 --> 40:04.599
So, somebody's answering
your brother's phone?

40:04.600 --> 40:06.550
Someone picked up the phone?

40:07.660 --> 40:09.419
I've been wanting to cancel the account

40:09.420 --> 40:13.179
but I know Mom likes to call
and hear his voice, that's why.

40:13.180 --> 40:15.109
She must be hallucinating, huh?

40:15.110 --> 40:15.943
Stop it!

40:15.943 --> 40:16.877
It happens.

40:16.878 --> 40:18.044
Stop!

40:30.170 --> 40:31.909
Oh, hello!

40:31.910 --> 40:32.743
Hi.

40:33.648 --> 40:36.199
I'm Wallace, I'm Madison's brother.

40:36.200 --> 40:37.713
Oh, I'm Samara,

40:38.980 --> 40:40.387
Elenie's beautiful mother.

40:41.596 --> 40:43.191
Are you hungry, Mr. Wallace?

40:43.192 --> 40:44.275
Okay, cool.

40:52.740 --> 40:53.989
Ooh!

40:53.990 --> 40:56.079
Holiday is a great deal to me,

40:56.080 --> 40:58.199
and Christmas is a big
holiday in Ethiopia.

40:58.200 --> 40:59.913
Oh, it's a big deal here too.

41:01.090 --> 41:03.239
Your wife needs to feed you better.

41:03.240 --> 41:04.519
You are too skinny!

41:04.520 --> 41:05.999
Ah!

41:06.000 --> 41:10.739
Well, that would be tough
because she doesn't exist.

41:10.740 --> 41:11.573
Oh.

41:13.189 --> 41:14.443
My son is your age.

41:17.440 --> 41:18.993
Oh, does he live nearby?

41:20.000 --> 41:20.833
No.

41:23.040 --> 41:25.557
