accident six months ago.

41:27.010 --> 41:27.843
I'm sorry.

41:29.040 --> 41:30.459
That's awful.

41:30.460 --> 41:31.293
I'm...

41:34.262 --> 41:35.163
He was a doctor,

41:36.950 --> 41:38.763
Doctor Abell Tariku.

41:40.660 --> 41:42.063
They called him Doctor AT.

41:43.145 --> 41:45.153
That's good, Doctor AT.

41:46.910 --> 41:49.879
I called his cell phone
and somebody answered.

41:49.880 --> 41:50.763
