41:51.710 --> 41:53.310
His cell phone is still working?

41:54.190 --> 41:55.583
Somebody's using it.

41:58.340 --> 41:59.173
Oh!

41:59.174 --> 42:00.409
Are you all done, Madison?

42:00.410 --> 42:01.559
Yeah, let's go.
All right.

42:01.560 --> 42:02.709
Bye, Maddie, Merry Christmas.

42:02.710 --> 42:03.779
