42:38.980 --> 42:40.647
Rasherzees?

42:41.481 --> 42:42.314
I don't know.

42:42.314 --> 42:43.257
Rorschach?

42:43.258 --> 42:45.123
Ah, yeah, well, they were stupid.

42:47.947 --> 42:49.099
Everything cool?

42:49.100 --> 42:49.933
