43:12.330 --> 43:15.989
What we have here is
the rare South African donkey

43:15.990 --> 43:17.114
known as the smartass.
No, you're weird.

43:17.115 --> 43:17.948
You're weird.

43:17.949 --> 43:19.016
To be perfectly honest, you do look

43:19.017 --> 43:20.859
pretty stupid right now.
I am not stupid.

43:20.860 --> 43:22.652
No, you look super stupid.
You're stupid.

43:22.653 --> 43:23.486
No!

43:25.939 --> 43:27.349
Thank you for your call.

43:27.350 --> 43:30.632
Sorry we couldn't meet in my
office, is everything okay?

43:30.633 --> 43:33.223
I got this note from Charley's teacher.

43:34.290 --> 43:35.619
Oh, another note?

43:35.620 --> 43:37.229
She seems like
a really nice lady.

43:37.230 --> 43:38.837
What strike now?

43:41.016 --> 43:43.163
I don't know, I could
use some advice, I guess.

43:46.581 --> 43:48.229
So are you and your wife ready

43:48.230 --> 43:51.139
to start family therapy, or?

43:51.140 --> 43:54.501
I think his teacher's
overreacting, I mean, don't you?

43:54.502 --> 43:56.236
I mean, come on, Charley's not,

43:56.237 --> 43:57.619
you know, he's not a bad kid.

43:57.620 --> 43:59.629
Then you should give it some time.

43:59.630 --> 44:01.380
Time will tell, things will change.

44:05.500 --> 44:08.090
I just want him to be happy, you know?

44:08.091 --> 44:08.924
Sure.

44:13.781 --> 44:17.212
Are you all right?

44:17.213 --> 44:19.630
I'm just hungry.

44:19.631 --> 44:20.828
Me too.

44:20.829 --> 44:23.496
Oh, here comes our food, cool.

44:24.600 --> 44:25.433
Oh, wow!

44:26.700 --> 44:27.533
It's colorful.

44:29.589 --> 44:31.229
Enjoy.
Thanks.

44:31.230 --> 44:32.709
She forgot the forks.

44:32.710 --> 44:37.019
Oh, we don't have forks,
we use our hands.

44:37.020 --> 44:37.853
All right.

44:37.854 --> 44:39.663
So you're gonna
have to try something new.

44:39.664 --> 44:40.593
Okay.

44:41.770 --> 44:42.603
Sounds fun.

44:42.604 --> 44:44.899
This is what we call
Injera, it's like our bread.

44:44.900 --> 44:46.149
Injera.

44:46.150 --> 44:49.667
It's made with a tiny grain
that grows in Ethiopia only.

44:49.668 --> 44:51.093
It's called Teff.

44:52.930 --> 44:53.993
It's gluten-free.

44:57.269 --> 45:00.809
And then you just put it in your mouth.

45:00.810 --> 45:02.699
What's this, is this lentils?

45:02.700 --> 45:03.640
Mm-hmm.

45:03.641 --> 45:04.949
I'm learning more about this.

45:04.950 --> 45:07.372
No, it's okay.

45:07.373 --> 45:09.140
That is so good!

45:09.141 --> 45:09.974
You like it?

45:09.975 --> 45:11.485
Wow, that is amazing!

45:11.486 --> 45:12.653
Yeah?
Yeah!

45:54.421 --> 45:55.254
Hey.

45:57.390 --> 45:58.542
You know what I miss?

45:58.543 --> 45:59.376
What?

46:01.790 --> 46:03.790
Being your girlfriend.

46:06.834 --> 46:08.703
What do I have to do

46:08.704 --> 46:10.702
to get you to take me out on a hot date?

46:16.245 --> 46:17.141
Ask.

46:35.557 --> 46:36.390
I...

47:06.543 --> 47:10.640
Didn't he, like, light his
textbook on fire, or something?

47:10.641 --> 47:11.842
Logan, grow up.

47:11.843 --> 47:13.759
I'm just saying, you know,

47:13.760 --> 47:16.273
let's just not leave him
alone, let's stay home.

47:18.520 --> 47:19.933
Two hours of TV.

47:20.821 --> 47:22.119
Mom!
Thank you so much.

47:22.120 --> 47:22.963
Don't Mom me.

47:24.518 --> 47:26.526
Listen to me, you see
this guy right here?

47:26.527 --> 47:29.754
If you see him with a
book, I want you to go

47:29.755 --> 47:30.637
to the neighbor's house...
Neighbor.

47:33.407 --> 47:34.340
You look slamming, Mila.

47:34.341 --> 47:37.283
Oh, thank you for noticing.

47:38.840 --> 47:40.648
I noticed.
Yeah, sure you did.

47:40.649 --> 47:41.649
I noticed!

47:57.240 --> 47:59.169
Only let me have two.

47:59.170 --> 48:00.889
I've heard that before.

48:00.890 --> 48:01.723
What is that supposed to mean?

48:01.724 --> 48:04.831
It means you are your own boss, baby.

48:06.860 --> 48:07.693
Hey.

48:07.693 --> 48:08.526
Hi, how you doing?

48:08.527 --> 48:10.063
Great, how are you?

48:10.064 --> 48:12.449
Very well.

48:12.450 --> 48:14.849
Two tequila shots, please, chilled.

48:14.850 --> 48:15.751
Coming right up.

48:21.361 --> 48:22.300
Thank you.

48:30.486 --> 48:31.375
Come on.

48:51.410 --> 48:52.243
That's two.

48:53.639 --> 48:55.549
Hold that thought.

48:55.550 --> 48:56.717
I have to pee.

48:57.860 --> 49:01.129
Are you sure you're allowed
to have these before dinner?

49:01.130 --> 49:02.927
I won't tell if you won't tell.

49:07.850 --> 49:09.909
Did you do this crash drawing?

49:09.910 --> 49:10.743
Yeah.

49:11.720 --> 49:13.520
Sucks to be that subway.

49:17.628 --> 49:19.298
Hey.

49:31.733 --> 49:32.999
Oh, my God!

49:33.000 --> 49:34.569
Hey!
Logan

49:34.570 --> 49:35.889
Thompson, hey!

49:35.890 --> 49:38.459
Hi, buddy, this is my spot.

49:38.460 --> 49:39.293
Are you serious?

49:39.294 --> 49:40.779
I come here too all the time.

49:40.780 --> 49:41.949
Well, we live right around the corner.

49:41.950 --> 49:42.950
Brooklyn for you.

49:42.951 --> 49:45.100
Brooklyn!

49:45.101 --> 49:46.649
What are you doing here by yourself?

49:46.650 --> 49:47.620
No, I'm not by myself.

49:47.621 --> 49:49.161
My wife is in the bathroom.

49:49.162 --> 49:50.299
Oh, okay, okay.
Yeah.

49:50.300 --> 49:51.969
I'm here with my girlfriend as well.

49:51.970 --> 49:53.113
How's Charley again?

49:54.160 --> 49:55.810
Charley's good, Charley's good.

49:57.810 --> 49:59.894
So you know how to dance?
How's your mom?

49:59.895 --> 50:01.208
Good.

50:01.209 --> 50:02.639
I want to see you do some moves!

50:02.640 --> 50:03.530
I can do some moves.
Come on, show me.

50:03.531 --> 50:04.709
You want some of these moves?

50:04.710 --> 50:05.543
Yeah.

50:06.870 --> 50:08.477
Oh, wow, '80s, huh?

50:08.478 --> 50:11.599
Oh, my God, I'm so sorry.

50:11.600 --> 50:12.683
Don't let me dance.

50:14.575 --> 50:16.635
I don't know, I'm sorry.

50:16.636 --> 50:17.605
Mila!

50:17.605 --> 50:18.438
Mila, hey!

50:20.064 --> 50:20.897
This is my wife.

50:20.898 --> 50:22.202
Mila, this is Elenie.

50:22.203 --> 50:23.719
This is Charley's counselor.

50:23.720 --> 50:28.669
I'm really sorry that I
haven't been by to see you,

50:28.670 --> 50:31.369
but I started a new job at the hospital

50:31.370 --> 50:32.720
and it's just been so busy.

50:34.409 --> 50:35.576
I'm a bad mom.

50:35.577 --> 50:38.459
No, no.
That's not true.

50:38.460 --> 50:39.430
Okay, I need another drink.

50:39.431 --> 50:41.928
Oh, this is my friend, Ayana.

50:41.929 --> 50:42.762
Hi.
Hey.

50:42.762 --> 50:43.595
Mr. and Mrs. Thompson.

50:43.595 --> 50:44.428
How are you?
Very nice to meet you.

50:44.429 --> 50:45.849
I'm propping her up with my elbow.

50:45.850 --> 50:46.790
Oh, okay, would you like another drink?

50:46.791 --> 50:48.489
I do.
Yeah, okay, come on.

50:48.490 --> 50:49.862
I want another drink.

50:49.863 --> 50:51.589
What happened to two?

50:51.590 --> 50:55.599
Two happened to you.

50:55.600 --> 50:56.483
Be social.

50:57.710 --> 50:58.610
Wow, you...

50:58.611 --> 51:00.549
She's just being social.

51:00.550 --> 51:03.329
Maybe I should do that.

51:03.330 --> 51:04.200
Why not?

51:04.201 --> 51:05.699
I can let go a little bit,

51:05.700 --> 51:08.711
but it's kinda hard when you're
a psychologist, you know,

51:08.712 --> 51:09.734
or a counselor.

51:09.735 --> 51:11.299
I bet you could find a way.

51:11.300 --> 51:14.118
Sure, once in a while, but not always.

51:14.119 --> 51:14.952
What?

51:14.953 --> 51:16.244
Not always!

51:16.245 --> 51:18.909
Okay, this is my bad ear.

51:18.910 --> 51:20.238
Not always!

51:20.239 --> 51:23.279
Yeah, did you
make that dress yourself?

51:23.280 --> 51:24.954
No, I bought it.

51:24.955 --> 51:26.599
I don't know, I'm sorry.
Why?

51:26.600 --> 51:28.673
Do you think I make dresses
all the time or something?

51:28.674 --> 51:29.650
No, I just...
Just because I wear 'em?

51:29.651 --> 51:31.253
You just look talented.

51:32.140 --> 51:32.973
That's very nice of you.

51:32.974 --> 51:34.289
Oh, no worries.

51:34.290 --> 51:36.077
I'm ready to go right now!

51:37.284 --> 51:39.492
Kidding, both are for you.

51:39.493 --> 51:40.463
That's great.

51:41.480 --> 51:42.649
I'm gonna give you the better one.

51:42.650 --> 51:44.009
Okay, thank you.

51:44.010 --> 51:45.336
Cheers.
Cheers.

51:45.337 --> 51:46.686
Cheers.
Cheers.

51:46.687 --> 51:47.545
Cheers.
Cheers.

51:47.546 --> 51:48.969
Cheers.
Cheers.

51:48.970 --> 51:50.123
Cheers.
Oh, cheers!

51:51.510 --> 51:53.763
Cheers.

51:56.008 --> 51:58.209
You don't need it, come on.

51:58.210 --> 51:59.043
Baby, eh!

52:02.019 --> 52:03.439
What happened to two drinks?

52:07.620 --> 52:09.929
What happened to being my own boss?

52:12.899 --> 52:14.089
Right, no, come on!

52:14.090 --> 52:16.535
What are you doing, what are you doing?

52:16.536 --> 52:17.690
What are you doing?

52:23.536 --> 52:24.758
I'm really sorry, I'm really sorry.

52:24.759 --> 52:25.818
What are you sorry about?

52:25.819 --> 52:26.977
Come on, come on.
What?

52:26.978 --> 52:28.579
What happened to two drinks, huh?

52:28.580 --> 52:29.430
Don't touch me!

52:30.576 --> 52:32.622
I'm trying to have a good time.

52:32.623 --> 52:34.639
Every time I have a good
time, you shit on it!

52:34.640 --> 52:35.473
I shit on it?

52:35.474 --> 52:37.259
Look, I'm sorry.

52:37.260 --> 52:39.269
What are you fucking apologizing for?

52:39.270 --> 52:41.849
I haven't been out since
my mother died, Logan!

52:41.850 --> 52:44.030
Who are you apologizing to?

52:44.031 --> 52:45.048
Fuck you!

52:48.636 --> 52:49.469
Fuck it!

52:54.617 --> 52:56.039
I think the heat's broken!

52:56.040 --> 52:56.873
Yup!

52:58.692 --> 52:59.525
Oh, man.

53:05.840 --> 53:06.673
No way!

53:10.759 --> 53:11.592
Oh!

53:13.440 --> 53:14.930
The king.

53:19.835 --> 53:22.813
Oh, man!

53:22.814 --> 53:23.647
Oh, I miss this.

53:36.340 --> 53:37.173
Doctor AT.

53:38.485 --> 53:39.318
Shit.

53:54.490 --> 53:56.883
Hey, can I get my tab closed out?

53:59.370 --> 54:01.471
Hey, is everything okay?

54:06.381 --> 54:07.414
She left her purse.

54:20.694 --> 54:22.011
Thank you for walking me home.

54:22.012 --> 54:23.108
Are you gonna be okay?

54:27.781 --> 54:29.297
I always am.

54:29.298 --> 54:30.215
You sure?

54:32.501 --> 54:33.334
What?

55:13.936 --> 55:15.237
You should go.

55:15.238 --> 55:16.140
You're right.

55:16.141 --> 55:18.668
You're right, this is,

55:18.669 --> 55:20.473
this is a horrible idea.

55:20.474 --> 55:21.307
I just,

55:22.752 --> 55:24.921
you're right, I should go home.

55:50.915 --> 55:52.027
This is really good.

56:55.477 --> 56:56.927
I'm sorry about last night.

57:00.040 --> 57:01.753
I guess I'm a piece of work, huh?

57:14.520 --> 57:17.643
Hey, did you see my purse from last night?

57:23.220 --> 57:24.053
I love you.

57:35.150 --> 57:37.453
Charley, what are your
soldiers looking for?

57:39.400 --> 57:40.233
Hmm?

57:42.020 --> 57:43.820
Are they looking for something cool?

57:45.820 --> 57:48.620
Charley, I know you're sad
about your grandmother dying.

57:49.930 --> 57:51.783
Someone close to me passed away too.

57:53.700 --> 57:55.300
Would you like to see a picture?

58:03.590 --> 58:06.363
This is my brother,
Abell, he was a doctor.

58:10.540 --> 58:11.683
Charley, are you okay?

58:12.620 --> 58:15.259
Charley, you don't have
to look at this picture.

58:15.260 --> 58:17.500
We'll do something else,
we'll try something else.

58:19.152 --> 58:19.985
You okay?

58:22.203 --> 58:23.036
What?

58:24.350 --> 58:27.229
Sorry, I didn't mean to scare you.

58:27.230 --> 58:28.063
The door was open.

58:28.064 --> 58:30.570
No, you didn't,
you didn't, I was just...

58:30.571 --> 58:32.154
Are you finished?

58:33.935 --> 58:35.189
Can I have a word with you, Elenie?

58:35.190 --> 58:37.529
Sure, of course.

58:37.530 --> 58:39.280
Charley, we'll be right back, okay?

58:40.620 --> 58:42.749
It's been really busy at
the hospital every night,

58:42.750 --> 58:46.763
and all of my spare time, I
just try to spend with Charley,

58:48.060 --> 58:49.919
and I'm just giving you excuses.

58:49.920 --> 58:52.239
You don't have to give me excuses.

58:52.240 --> 58:54.163
Logan wants what's best for Charley.

58:55.070 --> 58:58.106
I think that he wants to
be everything for him.

59:08.645 --> 59:11.379
What's wrong with my baby?

59:11.380 --> 59:14.469
He has anxiety
and suffers from depression.

59:14.470 --> 59:15.373
He's 11.

59:16.950 --> 59:18.463
He shows tendencies.

59:20.390 --> 59:22.039
I'm so bored, my brain hurts.

59:22.040 --> 59:24.584
I know, honey, one minute.

59:24.585 --> 59:25.418
Go.

59:25.419 --> 59:27.749
